OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian influencers to be  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbound by tighter rules     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italian social media creators could    
OL,6, soon be bound by the same rules as     
OL,7, traditional media outlets when posting 
OL,8, their content online.                  
OL,10,FThe activities of influencers are set  
OL,11,Fto come under the oversight of the     
OL,12,FItalian Communications Authority       
OL,13,F(AGCOM), it has said.                  
OL,15,FThe rules will initially apply to      
OL,16,Fcontent creators with more than one    
OL,17,Fmillion followers.                     
OL,19,F"The Wild West of influencers is over,"
OL,20,FAGCOM boss Giacomo Lasorella said.     
